	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Ok, I think you need to realize something. Every class in the game has its ups and downs. ex. rogues fast and deal a lot of damage=low hps and somewhat low AC. ex Warriors tank, Most hps in the game, Highest AC in the game, down side, they really dont deal a whole heck of a lot of damage at higher lvls compared to some classes. ex Monks, BIGGEST damage dealers in the game, Decent hps, low armor class. Id say its pretty well balanced out. If monks got higher AC items, that equal what a warrior gets, then the game would be entirely made up of Monks and a couple shammies and clerics. Plz for everyone elses sake, stop crying, and play the class that you have chosen, if you want higher ac, be a warrior, but dont expect to do as much damage as your monk. <br><br>P.S. Monks pull with FD to break camps, once the mob is back to the group, guess who generally tanks it? YOU got it!! The warrior. laters<br>&nbsp;<br>I just bought my computer today, i had some trouble turning it on, but i think i got it figured out!</td></tr>
